**Bug report 4\. \- Benefiti profile picture**

**Title/Summary:** In the “Kompanijski benefiti/Company benefits” tab, the profile picture cannot be changed or added in the benefit group editing tab.

**Description:** When creating or editing a benefit group, only the cover image is available to upload. When looking at all benefits groups, the mentioned benefit group has a random profile picture, in this case, some kind of email (see pictures below).![][image1]![][image2]

   
**Environment:** Desktop, Windows 10 (64-bit), Google Chrome 136.0.7103.114 (Official Build)

**Precondition:** Logged in as HR

**Steps to Reproduce:**

1. Go to [https://demo.benefiti.rs/?\#/company-benefits](https://demo.benefiti.rs/?#/company-benefits).  
2. Click on the big blue square button saying “Add company benefit group” or “Dodaj kompanijsku benefit grupu”.  
3. Fill in all of the mandatory fields.   
4. Upload a picture.  
5. Click on the second option in the blue navbar on the left, saying “Benefits” or “Benefiti”

**Expected Results:** In the benefit creating functionality, the HR user does not have the option to add or change the profile picture of the benefit group.

**Actual Results:** Only one field is available to upload a picture, and that picture is used as the cover photo. The profile photo is randomly chosen by the system.

**Severity: Low**

**Priority:** **Medium**
